## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of juvenile crime. The findings are limited to the perspectives and data provided by the sources reviewed. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of juvenile delinquency. Additionally, cultural and regional differences in juvenile crime were not extensively covered in this report.